# funding
 
 - funding of building free mesh networks for rural broad band equity
 - funding of workforce development on machining, electronics, networking, web development
 - funding from local business development money, chambers of commerce etc to support localized economy
 - direct grants from high net worth individuals for the Big Picture
 - climate mitigation money for eliminating global supply chain of materials using oil
 - research grants to develop new technologies like fabrication in slime for upcycled interconnects
 - small scale business investment to increase the profitability of small scrap businesses(banks, local investors, state loans and grants)
 - large scale climate and environmental NGO funding for the Big Picture
 - DOE money for the energy work, stirling engines made from trash to make stirling engines made from trash 
